OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry with cloud clearing and winds
OL,7,Feasing to light for most places. A
OL,8,Fmild night in urban areas but notably
OL,9,Fcooler in rural places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA bright and sunny day with
OL,12,Fjust a little patchy cloud around for
OL,13,Fsome places in the morning. Feeling
OL,14,Fwarm or very warm, with temperatures
OL,15,Fon the rise.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
