OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry,
OL,6,Fsunny and warm for most, though hot
OL,7,Ffor some on Monday. Expecting
OL,8,Ftemperatures to decrease Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday but still remaining above
OL,10,Faverage for the time of year.
